Overview
This application is a CRUD API built with FastAPI, SQLAlchemy, and Pydantic.
It allows you to Create, Read, Update, and Delete items in a database. The app also provides autoâ€‘generated documentation via Swagger UI (/docs) and ReDoc (/redoc).

Requirements
Install dependencies:
pip install fastapi uvicorn sqlalchemy pydantic

